# Objective

Validate the newly implemented Resource Profiling functionality to ensure:

- Resources are validated before sending requests to Bulk API.
- Global resource limits are enforced across all hierarchy paths.
- Only requests that fit within the configured resource pool become ACTIVE.
- Requests exceeding available resources move to WAITING_FOR_RESOURCE.
- Waiting requests are automatically processed by the scheduler when resources become available.
- Resource tracking records are updated correctly during the entire lifecycle.

