|----------|------------------|
| Executors | 3 |
| Executor Cores | 3 |
| Executor Memory | 4 GB |
| Driver Memory | 8 GB |
| Driver Cores | 1 |

**Note**

These are GLOBAL resources shared by all hierarchy paths.

Example:

If one report consumes

- Executors = 3
- Executor Cores = 3
- Executor Memory = 4 GB
- Driver Memory = 8 GB
- Driver Cores = 1

then no other report should become ACTIVE until this report releases the resources.

